commit.message: Deprecate old com.kenai.jnr versions of code
Kill off nbproject and ant build
Change to standard maven source dir layout
Revert java version to MIT license, same as asmjit
Add CpuInfo to select some cpu-specific optimizations
Convert some doxygen comments to javadoc
Remove canEmit(), since it is unused
Reformat some of the simpler methods
Use intValue() instead of an inline ternary (? 1 : 0) expression
